column1: [Highlight] Kevin Durant returns from a 2 month absence, does not miss a shot all night but Wenyen Gabriel steals the show with a spectacular sequence of certified sauce
[Owczarski] The Bucks have waived Wenyen Gabriel, Jalen Lecque, Javin DeLaurier and Tremont Waters.
[Smith] The New Orleans Pelicans have waived James Banks, Wenyen Gabriel and Malcolm Hill.
